refsection.programlisting:
// quit Scilab function foo(x) if x then quit end endfunction foo(%t) //quits scilab
//terminate instruction started in a pause context function foo(x) if x then quit end endfunction pause foo(%t) //returns at the main prompt level
function foo1(x) mprintf('P1\n') if x then pause mprintf('P2\n') end mprintf('P3\n') endfunction
foo1(%t) //enter quit at the following prompt
